Eirukna hi politics-a thil awmze nei tak niin a lang a, politician-te chuan mipui rawngbawl ai chuan an pocket lining hi an ngaihtuah zawk a ni.
Politician-te chu nitin mite harsatna lakah an him lo niin a lang fo va, anmahni privileged bubble-ah an khawsa a ni.
Political system-ah hian inefficiency, bureaucracy, leh red tape-in ​​a khat a, chu chuan inthlak danglamna \ha eng pawh a tikhawtlai a ni.
Lobbyist leh special interest group-te hian vote neitute aiin thuneihna an nei tam zawk a, hei hian democracy kalphung a tichhe hle.
Political debate hi thil tak tak chungchang thupui (substantive discussion of reality) aiin mudslinging leh personal attack-ah a innghat zawk a ni.
Campaign financing hi eirukna pianna hmun a ni a, mimal hausa leh corporation te pawhin influence an lei thei a ni.
Political polarization hi a nasa lutuk a, inremna leh inremna hmuh chu thil theih loh tluk a ni.
Media hian politics sensationalize-na kawngah hmun pawimawh tak a chang a, informative reporting aiin drama hi a dah pawimawh zawk a ni.
Inthlanna kalpui dan hi vote neitute tihbuai, gerrymandering leh democracy principle tichhe thei thil dangin a tichhe a ni.
Political hruaitute hian accountability an tlachham fo a, thutiam bawhchhiatna leh policy hlawhchhamnaah a rah chhuah tlemte chauh a awm.

Politician-te hian ṭhatna nasa zawk atana thutlukna khirh tak tak, mahse a tul tak tak siam ai chuan inthlanpui neih nawn leh hi an ngaihtuah zawk a ni.
Politics-a bureaucracy hi a buaithlak em em a, policy \ha tak tak kalpui a tikhawtlai a ni.

Political hruaitute hian an rawngbawl tur mipui chi hrang hrangte mamawh leh ngaihtuahna aiin an party an dah pawimawh zawk fo thin.
Political discourse chu tawp ngai lo, thumal hring (empty rhetoric) cycle-ah a inthlak a, substance leh actionable plan tlemte chauh a awm.
Politics leh corporation lian tak takte inkara kawngkhar inher chhuak hian duhdan inthlauhna a thlen a, mipui hlawkna a tichhe bawk.

Electoral college kalphung hian mi pakhat, vote pakhat tih principle a tichhe a, mipui duhdan dik tak a tichhe bawk.
Political appointment-ah hian thiamna aiin rinawmna a dah pawimawh zawk fo a, chu chuan hruaitu hlawhtling lo leh tling lo a thlen fo thin.
International diplomacy hi khawvel pum huap thawhhona leh remna zawnga inpekna dik tak aiin mahni hmasialna avanga kalpui a ni fo thin.
Political debate-ah hian nuance a tlachham fo va, thil buaithlak tak takte chu a awlsam lutuk a, mipui a hruai sual fo bawk.
